Package DetectAdjacentProperties

package DetectAdjacentProperties
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    AdjacencyDetector
    The AdjacencyDetector class is responsible for detecting adjacent properties based on their polygon coordinates.
    AdjacentPropertyPair
    The AdjacentPropertyPair class represents a pair of adjacent properties identified by their IDs.
    CoordinateFinder
    The CoordinateFinder class provides utility methods to find the maximum and minimum X and Y coordinates from a list of PropertyPolygon objects.
    MaxCoordinateFinder
    Deprecated.
    This class is deprecated and will be removed in a future release.
    MinCoordinateFinder
    Deprecated.
    This class is deprecated and will be removed in a future release.
    PropertyMerger
    The PropertyMerger class provides functionality to merge adjacent properties with the same owner into unified properties.
    PropertyOwnership
    Deprecated.
    TestUtils
    Utility class providing helper methods for creating test data and graphs used in unit tests for the DetectAdjacentProperties package.
